content:
On 31 January 2021 a Mw5.6 earthquake occurred in Southern Guyana near the border with Brazil (in the middle of a Precambrian shield). Join @EGU_Seismo on the #EGUblogs as the Earthquake Watch team find out why this #earthquake is so unusual.

Read more: https://t.co/cp8OdihtYT https://t.co/l70KLVjuWS
